# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AI Pandit — Docker Build Context Ignore
# Reduces build context from ~500MB to ~5MB for 10x faster builds.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Version control
.git
.gitignore

# Dependencies (re-installed in Docker)
node_modules
**/node_modules

# Build outputs (rebuilt in Docker)
dist
**/dist
.next
**/.next
.turbo
**/.turbo
out
build

# Environment files (secrets passed via env vars at runtime)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
!.env.example

# Docs (not needed in production image)
*.md
**/*.md
docs/
tasks/
scripts/
backend/
ephe/README.md

# Logs & misc
*.log
logs/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.eslintcache
.prettierrc
*.tsbuildinfo
.vercel
.idx
.gemini
.vscode
.cursorrules

# Tests & IDE
e2e/
playwright.config.ts
vitest.config.ts
vitest.workspace.ts
jest.config.js
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Tests (not needed in production image)
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/*.test.js
**/*.test.jsx
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.tsx
**/*.spec.js
**/*.spec.jsx
**/__tests__
**/tests
**/coverage
.nyc_output

# Frontend (backend-only Docker image)
apps/web

# Logs & misc
*.log
logs/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.eslintcache
.prettierrc
*.tsbuildinfo
.vercel
